model.agent.humanAgent.operationalLevel.action.movement

Class HelbingModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.agent.humanAgent.operationalLevel.action.movement.MovementModel
      • model.agent.humanAgent.operationalLevel.action.movement.HelbingModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Updatable

    public class HelbingModel
extends MovementModel
    The Helbing Model is an implementation of the Helbing (2000) paper. It uses 'social forces' to determine the next move.
    Author:
    S.A.M. Janssen
